        "output": "{'id': 'res_002', 'name': 'Bob Martinez', 'yoe_react': 1, 'yoe_python': 1, 'education': 'BA English Literature, San Francisco State University (2018). General Assembly fullstack web development bootcamp (3 months, 2023). No formal CS coursework.', 'highlights': 'Currently transitioning from a successful 4-year customer support and account management career at IBM Cloud. Self-taught web development since January 2024 - built 2 portfolio projects: a personal blog (Next.js, 200 LOC) and a recipe-tracking app (React + Firebase, deployed via Vercel). Active in #100DaysOfCode and aspires to reach junior fullstack within 18 months. Looking for an entry-level opportunity that values motivation over credentials. Strong communication skills from 4 years of B2B customer-facing work. Available for full-time start within 4 weeks.'}",
